The sample space \[CapitalOmega] has six outcomes ",
 StyleBox["a",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ", ",
 StyleBox["b",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ", ",
 StyleBox["c",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ", ",
