  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{"b", ",", "c", ",", "d", ",", "e"}], "}"}], TraditionalForm]]],
 ".  For a given number of trials ",
 StyleBox["n",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ", your simulator should sample an outcome from \[CapitalOmega] according to \
the given probabilities, and it should return the proportion of times, among \
